00:31:58,690 --> 00:31:59,816
[Thud]

401
00:31:59,925 --> 00:32:02,655
沒有了愛...
O'BRIEN: [Echoing] Without love...

402
00:32:02,728 --> 00:32:06,289
呼吸只不過是...擺動的時鐘
breath is just a clock... ticking.

403
00:32:06,331 --> 00:32:08,822
[Flames roaring]

404
00:32:08,867 --> 00:32:10,459
[Gasps]

405
00:32:10,535 --> 00:32:14,301
[Breathing heavily]

406
00:32:14,373 --> 00:32:17,865
[Heart beating]

407
00:32:32,290 --> 00:32:35,487
[Thunder rumbles]

408
00:32:47,539 --> 00:32:50,099
[Thunder rumbles]

409
00:32:50,175 --> 00:32:52,541
[Breathing heavily]

410
00:33:11,730 --> 00:33:13,891
[Thunder rumbles]

411
00:33:39,424 --> 00:33:41,085
[Whirs]

412
00:33:47,566 --> 00:33:51,559
波西安...解憂良藥
DUPONT: Prozium... the great nepenthe.

413
00:33:51,637 --> 00:33:53,832
我們大眾的鎮靜劑
Opiate of our masses.

414
00:33:53,906 --> 00:33:56,500
我們偉大社會的粘著劑
Glue of our great society.

415
00:33:56,575 --> 00:33:58,668
救命良方
Salve and salvation,

416
00:33:58,744 --> 00:34:02,680
解救我們脫離哀傷苦海
it has delivered us from pathos, from sorrow,

417
00:34:02,748 --> 00:34:06,809
憂鬱和仇恨間的深邃壕溝
the deepest chasms of melancholy and hate.

418
00:34:06,885 --> 00:34:09,410
有了它,我們才能麻醉悲傷
With it, we anesthetize grief,

419
00:34:09,488 --> 00:34:13,584
摧毀嫉妒、消滅憤怒
annihilate jealousy, obliterate rage.

420
00:34:13,659 --> 00:34:18,096
那些修女鼓吹的喜、愛與和樂
That those sister impulses towards joy, love, and elation

421
00:34:18,163 --> 00:34:20,723
早已麻木了
are anesthetized in stride,

422
00:34:20,799 --> 00:34:23,097
我們認為是種合理的犧牲
we accept as fair sacrifice.

423
00:34:23,168 --> 00:34:29,129
因為我們可以完完全全地注射波西安
For we embrace Prozium in its unifying fullness

424
00:34:29,208 --> 00:34:33,440
它的效果使得我們日益強大
and all that it has done to make us great.

425
00:34:42,187 --> 00:34:44,178
[Loud footsteps]

426
00:35:26,465 --> 00:35:27,864
早安,教士
Good morning, Cleric.

427
00:35:27,933 --> 00:35:29,867
早安
Good morning.

428
00:35:29,935 --> 00:35:33,996
...基本上,人類乃地球上的生物
...intrinsically, humans, as creatures of the Earth

429
00:35:34,072 --> 00:35:40,307
到頭來總是回歸到一件事...戰爭
were drawn inherently always back to one thing... war.

430
00:35:40,379 --> 00:35:43,678
因此我們不能只治標
And thus we seek to correct not the symptom

431
00:35:43,749 --> 00:35:46,309
而是要治本
but the disease itself.

432
00:35:46,385 --> 00:35:49,843
我們得將個人拋諸度外
We have sought to shrug off individuality,

433
00:35:49,922 --> 00:35:52,550
取而代之為服從
replacing it with conformity.

434
00:35:52,624 --> 00:35:55,525
取而代之...
Replacing it...

435
00:35:55,594 --> 00:35:58,324
為平等...
with sameness...

436
00:35:58,397 --> 00:36:00,888
為統一
with unity,

437
00:36:00,966 --> 00:36:05,528
使得每個男人、女人、小孩
allowing each man, woman, and child

438
00:36:05,604 --> 00:36:07,435
加入這個大家庭中
in this great society

439
00:36:07,506 --> 00:36:11,067
過著完全相同的生活
to lead identical lives.

440
00:36:12,611 --> 00:36:16,103
此同等環境架構的基本概念
The concept of identical environment construction

441
00:36:16,181 --> 00:36:19,446
使得我們自信滿滿地迎接每一刻來臨
allows each of us to head confidently into each moment

442
00:36:19,518 --> 00:36:21,247
儘管這種安全理念
with all the secure knowledge

443
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:24,153
很早以前就有了
it has been lived before.

444
00:36:24,189 --> 00:36:26,623
[Voice fades]

445
00:36:38,971 --> 00:36:40,632
你在做什麼?
What are you doing?

446
00:36:44,443 --> 00:36:46,411
我在重新擺設我的桌子
I'm rearranging my desk.

447
00:36:46,478 --> 00:36:49,140
你不喜歡之前的樣子嗎?
You didn't like the way it was before?

448
00:36:50,782 --> 00:36:52,340
沒啥感覺
I had no feelings about it.

449
00:36:52,417 --> 00:36:54,612
我只是想充分運用空間
I'm merely attempting to optimize.

450
00:36:57,656 --> 00:37:01,524
感情罪犯窩藏在尼瑟斯裡
Sense offenders holed up in the Nether.

451
00:37:15,774 --> 00:37:18,607
我們估計...我們估計有50人,長官
We estimate... we estimate 50 men, sir.

452
00:37:18,677 --> 00:37:22,272
據收到情報,他們全部持有槍械
Intelligence tells us they're all fully armed.

453
00:37:22,348 --> 00:37:25,977
就是這群人去炸波西安製藥廠的
This is the group that bombed the Prozium factories.

454
00:37:26,051 --> 00:37:27,575
你們先沖,我們隨後掃蕩
You clean, we'll sweep.

455
00:37:27,653 --> 00:37:29,177
遵命,長官
Yes, sir.

456
00:37:29,254 --> 00:37:30,778
[Indistinct shouting]

457
00:37:32,191 --> 00:37:34,056
沖! 沖! 沖! 沖!
Go! Go! Go! Go!

458
00:37:34,126 --> 00:37:35,058
沖!
Go!

459
00:37:35,127 --> 00:37:36,719
啊!
Aah!

460
00:37:36,795 --> 00:37:39,195
攻下! 攻佔樓梯間!
Take it! Take the landings!

461
00:37:40,399 --> 00:37:41,388
啊! 啊!
- Aah! - Aah!

462
00:37:52,878 --> 00:37:55,005
-掩護我,我要進去 -啊...!
- Cover me. I'm going in. - Aaaaaaaah!

463
00:37:58,884 --> 00:38:00,374
抓得好,教士
Nice grab, Cleric.

464
00:38:37,989 --> 00:38:40,423
[Casings rattling]

465
00:39:08,720 --> 00:39:10,381
[Door rattles, creaks]

466
00:39:12,457 --> 00:39:14,448
[Door opens]

467
00:39:15,794 --> 00:39:18,285
[Stairs creaking]

468
00:40:30,069 --> 00:40:33,971
"貝多芬"
"Ludwig Van Beethoven."

469
00:40:59,531 --> 00:41:01,522
[Record scratching]

470
00:41:28,593 --> 00:41:30,788
[Powerful classical music plays]

471
00:41:57,288 --> 00:41:59,347
[Music continues]

472
00:42:32,658 --> 00:42:33,818
教士...
Cleric...

473
00:42:34,860 --> 00:42:36,350
你為何不把那個留下
Why didn't you leave that

474
00:42:36,428 --> 00:42:39,192
給證物組的人採集登記?
for the evidentiary team to collect and log?

475
00:42:45,337 --> 00:42:46,770
他們偶爾會弄丟
They miss things sometimes.

476
00:42:46,839 --> 00:42:49,967
我自己拿著...
I'll take it in myself...

477
00:42:50,042 --> 00:42:52,840
比較保險
make sure it gets done properly.

478
00:42:54,679 --> 00:42:55,873
[Sighs]

479
00:42:55,948 --> 00:42:57,939
你知道,培斯頓...
You know, Preston...

480
00:42:59,685 --> 00:43:01,846
如果我們繼續燒燬這些違禁品
If we keep burning all this contraband,

481
00:43:01,920 --> 00:43:04,150
到最後就什麼也沒得燒了
eventually there won't be anything left to burn.

482
00:43:04,223 --> 00:43:08,023
那像我們這種人還能幹什麼?
What'll there be for men like us?

483
00:43:08,093 --> 00:43:09,788
長官!
Sir!

484
00:43:09,862 --> 00:43:11,420
後方有發現
We got something out back.

485
00:43:11,496 --> 00:43:13,020
[Men talking indistinctly]

486
00:43:20,973 --> 00:43:23,339
我們還需要多派兩人來處理
We're gonna need two more men on this.

487
00:43:27,378 --> 00:43:28,709
[Barking]

488
00:43:28,780 --> 00:43:31,112
這些動物是女人小孩所飼養的
These animals were defended by women and children.

489
00:43:31,183 --> 00:43:32,480
兩三下就解決掉了
We put them down easily.

490
00:43:32,551 --> 00:43:36,180
又不是第一次碰到這種事了
This isn't the first time we've seen this.

491
00:43:36,255 --> 00:43:38,519
他們幹嘛養這些動物?
Why do they keep these animals?

492
00:43:38,590 --> 00:43:40,717
怎麼,難道他們...吃它們嗎?
What, do they... do they eat them?

493
00:43:42,728 --> 00:43:44,855
你要我怎麼做,長官?
What do you want me to do, sir?

494
00:43:44,930 --> 00:43:46,227
當然是全數消滅
Exterminate them, of course.

495
00:43:46,298 --> 00:43:47,731
好了,動手吧
All right. Let's do it.

496
00:43:47,799 --> 00:43:49,562
不
- No. - [Guns cocking]

497
00:43:49,635 --> 00:43:50,829
怎麼了,教士?
What's wrong, Cleric?

498
00:43:54,406 --> 00:43:56,601
沒事
Nothing.

499
00:43:57,775 --> 00:43:59,538
[Barking continues]

500
00:44:02,313 --> 00:44:04,508
[Gunshots, dogs whimpering]

501
00:44:09,621 --> 00:44:11,111
嘿...
- Hey... - [Dog running]

502
00:44:11,189 --> 00:44:12,417
抓住它
Grab it.

503
00:44:12,491 --> 00:44:13,583
抓住它!
Grab it!

504
00:44:21,333 --> 00:44:23,528
長官...把它丟回去
Sir... toss it back in.

505
00:44:23,602 --> 00:44:25,433
我來解決掉它
I'll finish it off.

506
00:44:29,340 --> 00:44:30,272
[Gun cocks]

507
00:44:30,342 --> 00:44:31,366
把它交給我,長官
Give it to me, sir.

508
00:44:31,443 --> 00:44:33,377
交給他,教士,他會解決它的
Give it to him, Cleric. He'll finish it.

509
00:44:39,884 --> 00:44:42,114
[Whimpering]

510
00:44:44,555 --> 00:44:47,285
[Whimpering continues]

511
00:44:47,359 --> 00:44:48,621
等等!
Wait!

512
00:44:51,630 --> 00:44:54,190
我覺得...
It seems to me that...

513
00:44:54,266 --> 00:44:57,929
至少該留下一隻來做疾病測試
at least some of these animals ought to be tested for disease.

514
00:44:58,003 --> 00:45:00,028
如果尼瑟斯裡有傳染病
If there's an epidemic in the Nether,

515
00:45:00,105 --> 00:45:02,573
我們才好知道
it's best we know about it.

516
00:45:05,577 --> 00:45:09,343
我不太懂你的邏輯,教士
I don't quite follow your logic, Cleric.

517
00:45:09,414 --> 00:45:10,676
它們是反抗組織
They were Resistance.

518
00:45:10,748 --> 00:45:12,978
它們本可帶我們深入地下社會
They could have led us to the Underground.

519
00:45:13,051 --> 00:45:14,712
而非逮捕及審問
But instead of apprehension and interrogation,

520
00:45:14,786 --> 00:45:15,753
將它們全數殺光
they were slaughtered.

521
00:45:15,820 --> 00:45:18,983
是的,不過,教士,這種情形是...
Yes, but, Cleric, given the circumstances,

522
00:45:19,057 --> 00:45:20,649
神父早已下令過
the Father has decreed

523
00:45:20,725 --> 00:45:24,126
凡感情罪犯不再透過"訴訟程序"
that there will be no more "process" for sense offenders.

524
00:45:24,195 --> 00:45:26,595
不是當場格殺
They are either to be shot on sight

525
00:45:26,664 --> 00:45:28,154
就是不經審判直接火化
or incinerated without a trial.

526
00:45:28,232 --> 00:45:29,358
但那樣與法律背道而馳
But it's counter to law.

527
00:45:29,434 --> 00:45:31,265
你是議會一員,如果...
You're a member of the Council. If...

528
00:45:31,336 --> 00:45:33,201
這不是議會的旨意
It is not the will of the Council,

529
00:45:33,271 --> 00:45:36,035
是神父的旨意...他就是法律
it is the will of Father... and he is law.

530
00:45:37,675 --> 00:45:40,166
長官...
Sir...

531
00:45:40,244 --> 00:45:43,179
少了邏輯程序,豈不是成了濫殺無辜...
without the logic of process, is it not just mayhem...

532
00:45:43,247 --> 00:45:46,239
那何必如此賣力去撲殺呢?
what we have worked so hard to eradicate?

533
00:45:46,317 --> 00:45:48,444
你必須明白,培斯頓
You must understand, Preston,

534
00:45:48,519 --> 00:45:52,114
不管你或是我同不同意
that while you... and even I... may not always agree with it,

535
00:45:52,190 --> 00:45:54,886
都無關緊要
it is not the message that is important,

536
00:45:54,959 --> 00:45:58,190
重要的是服從
it is our obedience to it.

537
00:45:58,262 --> 00:46:00,389
神父的旨意
Father's will.

538
00:46:00,465 --> 00:46:03,059
稱之為信仰
Call it faith.

539
00:46:03,134 --> 00:46:05,159
我想你有吧?
You have it, I assume?

540
00:46:09,774 --> 00:46:11,105
是的
Yes.

541
00:46:12,610 --> 00:46:14,168
我有
I have it.

542
00:46:14,245 --> 00:46:15,803
很好
Good.

543
00:46:21,452 --> 00:46:23,443
[Click, whirring]

544
00:46:24,989 --> 00:46:26,718
[Click]

545
00:46:26,791 --> 00:46:30,352
[Click, whirring]

546
00:46:37,168 --> 00:46:40,501
收押證物X23-T45...
Confiscated evidence X23-T45...

547
00:46:40,571 --> 00:46:42,937
瑪麗·歐布萊恩
Mary O'Brien.

548
00:47:30,321 --> 00:47:32,255
[Exhales deeply]

549
00:47:40,431 --> 00:47:42,763
[Car engine revs]

550
00:47:45,069 --> 00:47:47,162
約翰·培斯頓教士進入尼瑟斯...
Cleric John Preston passing into the Nether...

551
00:47:47,238 --> 00:47:49,399
執行任務
enforcement-related.

552
00:47:52,410 --> 00:47:53,638
謝謝,長官
Thank you, sir.

553
00:48:23,007 --> 00:48:25,498
[Whimpers]

554
00:48:25,577 --> 00:48:28,205
我不知道還能拿你怎麼辦
I don't know what else to do with you.

555
00:48:31,082 --> 00:48:32,310
去吧
Go on.

556
00:48:32,383 --> 00:48:33,372
去吧
Go on.

557
00:48:33,451 --> 00:48:34,782
[Trunk door creaks]

558
00:48:34,852 --> 00:48:35,944
[Trunk door closes]

559
00:48:36,020 --> 00:48:37,817
快走!
Go!

560
00:48:38,923 --> 00:48:40,823
[Keys jingle]

561
00:48:47,198 --> 00:48:48,563
[Dog barks]

562
00:48:48,632 --> 00:48:49,997
[Panting]

563
00:48:54,271 --> 00:48:56,205
[Engine turns over]

564
00:48:57,241 --> 00:48:58,469
[Yelps]

565
00:49:06,083 --> 00:49:07,072
[Engine shuts off]

566
00:49:13,324 --> 00:49:14,450
好吧
Fine.

567
00:49:14,526 --> 00:49:16,551
不過你得待在後備箱裡
But you're going back in the trunk.

568
00:49:21,265 --> 00:49:22,425
[Yelps]

569
00:49:27,638 --> 00:49:28,730
[Chuckles]

570
00:49:30,408 --> 00:49:31,932
好吧
Okay.

571
00:49:35,246 --> 00:49:36,508
拿去
Here.

572
00:49:43,487 --> 00:49:44,818
[Engines revving]

573
00:49:47,892 --> 00:49:49,757
離開車子!
Step away from the vehicle!

574
00:49:49,827 --> 00:49:52,057
離開車子!
Step away from the vehicle!

575
00:49:52,130 --> 00:49:53,427
最後一次警告!
This is your last warning!

576
00:49:53,498 --> 00:49:56,331
離開車子!
Step away from the vehicle!

577
00:49:56,401 --> 00:49:58,596
證件
Identification.

578
00:49:58,670 --> 00:50:00,103
我是個教士
I'm a Cleric.

579
00:50:00,171 --> 00:50:02,366
我來辦官方事務的
I'm here on official business.

580
00:50:02,440 --> 00:50:03,202
證件!
Identification!

581
00:50:04,509 --> 00:50:05,601
在我外套裡
It's in my coat.

582
00:50:05,677 --> 00:50:07,907
外套在哪? 在哪?!
Where's the coat? Where is it?!

583
00:50:09,180 --> 00:50:11,239
我沒帶
I don't have it.

584
00:50:11,316 --> 00:50:14,046
有不明人士可能在進行破壞
Unidentified individuals are subject to summary destruction.

585
00:50:14,118 --> 00:50:15,779
你犯了個極大的錯誤
You're making a very big mistake.

586
00:50:15,853 --> 00:50:16,911
我是葛拉瑪頓教士,最高等級的
I'm a Grammaton Cleric, first class.

587
00:50:17,021 --> 00:50:18,010
我們要搜查你的車子
We're gonna search your vehicle.

588
00:50:18,089 --> 00:50:20,353
不,不用查,裡頭沒什麼
No, you're not. There's nothing in it.

589
00:50:20,425 --> 00:50:21,892
快搜!
Search it!

590
00:50:28,733 --> 00:50:30,667
-沒事,長官 -搜查後備箱
- Clear, sir. - Keys to the trunk.

591
00:50:30,735 --> 00:50:31,997
我一直告訴過你
I'm trying to tell you.

592
00:50:32,070 --> 00:50:34,129
我黎明前還得去見證火化
I have a predawn combustion to witness.

593
00:50:34,205 --> 00:50:35,638
我不是...
I'm not...

594
00:50:35,707 --> 00:50:37,675
隊長,這是在浪費我的時間
Captain, this is a waste of my time.

595
00:50:37,742 --> 00:50:39,073
我叫約翰·培斯頓
My name is John Preston.

596
00:50:39,143 --> 00:50:41,475
我是耶和華的最高等級教士...
I'm the highest-ranking Cleric of the Tetragramm...

597
00:50:41,546 --> 00:50:43,138
等等
Wait.

598
00:50:46,718 --> 00:50:47,776
站到一旁去
Stand off.

599
00:50:50,622 --> 00:50:53,022
抱歉沒認出你來,長官
I'm sorry I didn't recognize you, sir.

600
00:50:55,293 --> 00:50:57,557
沒關係,你們只是在執行勤務而已
That's okay. Just doing your job.

601
00:50:57,629 --> 00:50:58,618
謝謝
Thank you.

602
00:50:59,897 --> 00:51:01,558
我們會護送您回到門口
We'll escort you back to the gate.

603
00:51:01,633 --> 00:51:02,565
謝謝
Thanks.

604
00:51:02,633 --> 00:51:04,328
[Dog yelps]

605
00:51:09,774 --> 00:51:11,002
動物
Animals.

606
00:51:12,443 --> 00:51:13,910
尼瑟斯到處都是
Nether's full of them.

607
00:51:13,978 --> 00:51:15,878
聲音好像是從你的後備箱裡傳來的
Sounds like it came from your trunk.

608
00:51:15,947 --> 00:51:17,881
不可能
Impossible.

609
00:51:17,949 --> 00:51:19,883
把鑰匙給我好了
Just give me my keys.

610
00:51:19,951 --> 00:51:21,077
我會馬上離開
I'll be on my way.

611
00:51:26,758 --> 00:51:28,020
隊長...
Captain...

612
00:51:28,092 --> 00:51:31,220
我最後跟你再說一次...
I'm asking you one last time...

613
00:51:31,295 --> 00:51:33,092
不要這麼做
don't do this.

614
00:51:34,632 --> 00:51:35,894
跪下!
Down on your knees!

615
00:51:35,967 --> 00:51:37,559
- 跪下! - 跪下!
- Down on your knees! - Down on your knees!

616
00:51:37,635 --> 00:51:38,829
趴下!
Drop down!

617
00:51:38,903 --> 00:51:41,167
趴到地上!快!
On the ground! Comply!

618
00:51:41,239 --> 00:51:42,831
快點!
Do it!

619
00:51:43,574 --> 00:51:44,666
不
No.

620
00:51:44,742 --> 00:51:46,073
媽的!
Fuck!

621
00:51:50,481 --> 00:51:51,846
什麼?
What?

622
00:51:51,916 --> 00:51:54,214
啊,媽的!射他!射他!射他!
Aw, shit! Shoot him! Shoot him! Shoot him!

623
00:52:03,528 --> 00:52:04,722
啊!
Aah!

624
00:52:19,343 --> 00:52:21,334
[Casings rattling]

625
00:52:31,455 --> 00:52:34,049
[Wind blowing]

626
00:52:53,377 --> 00:52:55,436
[Exhales deeply]

627
00:54:08,485 --> 00:54:12,216
[Grunting]

628
00:54:23,067 --> 00:54:25,592
總是在練習, 教士
Always practicing, Cleric.

629
00:54:25,670 --> 00:54:28,332
我想這就是為什麼你是最好的吧
I guess that's why you're the best.

630
00:54:31,442 --> 00:54:33,034
可能我只是更好一點
Maybe I'm just better.

631
00:54:34,078 --> 00:54:35,909
在想心事嗎?
Something on your mind?

632
00:54:35,979 --> 00:54:38,504
[Both grunting]

633
00:54:38,583 --> 00:54:39,914
為什麼這麼問?
Why do you ask?

634
00:54:39,984 --> 00:54:41,246
直覺藝術, 教士
The intuitive arts, Cleric.

635
00:54:41,319 --> 00:54:43,412
我的職責就是知你所想
It's my job to know what you're thinking.

636
00:54:53,630 --> 00:54:54,722
[Mask thuds]

637
00:54:54,799 --> 00:54:57,461
那...我現在在想什麼?
So, then... what am I thinking?

638
00:55:02,440 --> 00:55:05,500
在想昨晚尼瑟斯的謀殺案...
About the murders in the Nether last night...

639
00:55:05,576 --> 00:55:07,737
[Whooshing]

640
00:55:11,849 --> 00:55:13,612
他們是否知道是誰做的
And if they know who did it.

641
00:55:13,684 --> 00:55:15,879
[Both grunting]

642
00:55:19,423 --> 00:55:20,447
我說的接近了嗎?
Am I close?

643
00:55:23,327 --> 00:55:25,795
那麼,告訴我...他們知道嗎?
So, tell me... do they know?

644
00:55:31,568 --> 00:55:34,366
[Panting]

645
00:55:34,438 --> 00:55:36,303
有一些猜測
There are theories.

646
00:55:36,374 --> 00:55:38,672
我自己也有幾種但是就目前來看...
I have one or two of my own, but at the moment...

647
00:55:38,743 --> 00:55:40,938
都不成熟!
[Straining] They're premature!

648
00:55:45,716 --> 00:55:47,081
我很高興發生了這件事
I'm glad it happened.

649
00:55:51,923 --> 00:55:52,514
為什麼?
Why?

650
00:55:52,590 --> 00:55:54,649
因為現在神父和教會
Because now Father and the Council

651
00:55:54,725 --> 00:55:58,252
頒布了加速鎮壓情感犯的法令
have decreed an acceleration in the crackdown on offenders.

652
00:55:58,329 --> 00:56:00,524
不管是誰做的...
Whoever did it...

653
00:56:00,598 --> 00:56:03,965
都是加速了叛軍的滅亡
all they accomplished was a quicker end to the Resistance.

654
00:56:13,411 --> 00:56:15,174
將會有場大屠殺的, 教士
It's gonna be a massacre, Cleric.

655
00:56:31,929 --> 00:56:35,126
我是來告訴你...在尼瑟斯有一場大搜捕...
I came to tell you... there's a raid in the Nether...

656
00:56:35,199 --> 00:56:38,225
7區
Sector 7.

657
00:56:38,302 --> 00:56:39,701
[Panting]

658
00:56:39,770 --> 00:56:41,863
準備一下吧
So get ready.

659
00:57:23,247 --> 00:57:24,612
從後面的門走...
That door behind you...

660
00:57:26,684 --> 00:57:28,049
走啊
Go.

661
00:57:29,687 --> 00:57:31,052
走啊,他媽的!
Go, damn you!

662
00:57:35,459 --> 00:57:37,120
離開這兒,天殺的! 如果你們不走就死定了!
Get out of here, God damn it! If you don't, you're dead!

663
00:57:37,194 --> 00:57:39,025
別聽他的. 他會從後面槍殺我們的
Don't do it. He'll shoot us in the back.

664
00:57:39,096 --> 00:57:41,064
如果我要槍殺你們, 我會面對面的做的
If I was gonna shoot you, I'd shoot you in the face.

665
00:57:41,132 --> 00:57:42,497
快走.
Now go.

666
00:57:48,672 --> 00:57:50,503
他媽的!跟我來
Damn you! Follow me.

667
00:57:50,574 --> 00:57:53,270
快!快走!
Now! Let's go!

668
00:58:02,353 --> 00:58:03,877
以後將不再拘留人犯
MAN: There will be no detention.

669
00:58:03,954 --> 00:58:07,754
再說一遍... 將不再用任何方式拘留人犯
Repeat... no detention for any purpose.

670
00:58:07,825 --> 00:58:11,625
所有人犯都將被處決.
All prisoners and apprehendees are to be put down.

671
00:58:19,236 --> 00:58:21,329
小心!
Look out!

672
00:58:24,141 --> 00:58:25,768
啊!
Aah!

673
00:58:27,912 --> 00:58:29,311
啊!
Aaaah!

674
00:58:33,818 --> 00:58:36,116
教士,出什麼事了? 我們聽到了槍聲
Cleric, what's happening? We heard gunshots.

675
00:58:37,688 --> 00:58:38,677
走!
Go!

676
00:58:38,756 --> 00:58:40,986
你在幹什麼? 教士!
What are you doing? Cleric!

677
00:58:41,058 --> 00:58:42,320
他們是叛軍
They're Resistance fighters.

678
00:58:43,360 --> 00:58:44,349
教士!
Cleric!

679
00:58:47,231 --> 00:58:48,357
他是個情感罪犯!
He's a sense offender!

680
00:59:29,039 --> 00:59:32,372
[Indistinct shouting]

681
00:59:32,476 --> 00:59:33,841
守住所有出口!
Cover all quadrants!

682
00:59:33,911 --> 00:59:35,242
四處搜查!
Secure the perimeter!

683
00:59:46,290 --> 00:59:47,757
怎麼回事?
What is this?

684
00:59:48,926 --> 00:59:50,723
你們在幹什麼?!
What are you doing?!

685
00:59:50,794 --> 00:59:53,354
做得好,教士
Nicely done, Cleric.

686
00:59:53,430 --> 00:59:55,489
你把他們趕進了陷阱...
You drive them into the trap...

687
00:59:57,501 --> 00:59:58,695
我來收口
I close it.

688
01:00:04,875 --> 01:00:09,869
真是典型的...團隊合作
The very definition of... teamwork.

689
01:00:09,947 --> 01:00:11,471
你不覺得麼?
Don't you think?

690
01:00:13,951 --> 01:00:17,079
你為什麼不享受一下親手處決 他們的榮譽呢,教士?
Why don't you take the honors of the execution, Cleric?

691
01:00:20,824 --> 01:00:23,987
這些人應該被送去臨床審查
These people should be taken for clinical interrogation.

692
01:00:24,061 --> 01:00:25,221
教士...
Cleric...

693
01:00:25,296 --> 01:00:27,594
神父的指示非常明確
Father's rulings are quite clear.

694
01:00:27,665 --> 01:00:30,429
罪犯們應被當場槍決
Offenders are to be shot on sight.

695
01:00:30,501 --> 01:00:32,059
他們有很有價值的情報
They have valuable information.

696
01:00:32,136 --> 01:00:33,160
教士...
Cleric...

697
01:00:33,237 --> 01:00:34,727
留著他們還有更大的用處
They can be put to much better use.

698
01:00:34,805 --> 01:00:35,772
教士
Cleric.

699
01:00:37,107 --> 01:00:40,907
如果你的彈藥不夠, 請用我的
If your weapon's low, please, use mine.

700
01:00:59,896 --> 01:01:02,194
[Gun cocks]

701
01:01:30,127 --> 01:01:30,821
不
No.

702
01:01:34,131 --> 01:01:36,622
我覺得,還是...
I think, in the end...

703
01:01:36,700 --> 01:01:38,759
你自己來比較好
it'll be better if you have it.

704
01:02:00,991 --> 01:02:01,980
隊長
Captain.

705
01:02:02,059 --> 01:02:04,050
是,長官.準備射擊
Yes, sir. Firing positions.

706
01:02:08,299 --> 01:02:09,561
預備...
CAPTAIN: Ready...

707
01:02:09,599 --> 01:02:11,260
[Guns cocking]

708
01:02:18,409 --> 01:02:19,376
瞄準...
Aim...

709
01:02:26,150 --> 01:02:27,947
射擊!
Fire!

710
01:02:27,984 --> 01:02:29,144
[Gunfire]

711
01:02:29,219 --> 01:02:30,811
[Men screaming]

712
01:02:34,658 --> 01:02:36,455
長官?
PRESTON: Sir?

713
01:02:36,527 --> 01:02:38,358
什麼事, 教士?
Yes, Cleric?

714
01:02:38,429 --> 01:02:41,227
你叫我做神父的
You asked me to become Father's instrument

715
01:02:41,298 --> 01:02:43,994
鎮壓叛亂的工具
against the Resistance.

716
01:02:44,068 --> 01:02:46,002
我準備好了
I'm ready.

717
01:02:46,070 --> 01:02:48,004
今天
Today.

718
01:02:48,072 --> 01:02:49,869
我想表現一下我的忠誠
I wish to show my faith.

719
01:02:51,975 --> 01:02:53,840
我想,在您的許可下
I wish, with your permission,

720
01:02:53,911 --> 01:02:56,812
去徹底查出地下組織的根據地
to locate the Underground once and for all.

721
01:02:56,880 --> 01:02:58,347
以便摧毀它
To destroy it.

722
01:03:01,118 --> 01:03:02,710
以便摧毀它
To destroy it.

723
01:03:02,786 --> 01:03:04,879
好,你去做吧
Good. Do it.

724
01:03:14,299 --> 01:03:17,291
我非常...
I'm so...

725
01:03:17,368 --> 01:03:19,131
非常抱歉
so very sorry.

726
01:03:30,782 --> 01:03:34,081
這是他死時帶在身上的東西
These are the possessions he had on him at the time of death.

727
01:03:34,152 --> 01:03:35,551
非法的東西將跟他一起被焚化
The illegal ones will be burned with him.

728
01:03:35,620 --> 01:03:36,917
好
Good.

729
01:04:18,496 --> 01:04:19,827
艾洛·帕崔吉
Errol Partridge.

730
01:04:23,801 --> 01:04:26,099
這個名字對我應該有意義嗎?
The name supposed to mean something to me?

731
01:04:26,170 --> 01:04:28,934
他曾是秩序、教士, 一流的,你認識他
He was a Grammaton Cleric, first class. You knew him.

732
01:04:29,007 --> 01:04:32,272
新聞公告 ... 我是個情感罪犯
News bulletin... I'm a sense offender.

733
01:04:32,343 --> 01:04:34,504
我不跟教士們在一起的
I don't hang around much with the Cleric.

734
01:04:41,252 --> 01:04:43,277
我想知道他的事
I want to know about him.

735
01:04:46,557 --> 01:04:47,819
好吧...
Well...

736
01:04:47,892 --> 01:04:50,986
我建議你自己去問他
I suggest you go ask him.

737
01:04:52,096 --> 01:04:55,065
但我知道他已經死了...
But I understand that he's dead...

738
01:04:55,133 --> 01:04:58,762
被你在耶和華的朋友殺死的
killed by your friends at the Tetragrammaton.

739
01:04:58,836 --> 01:05:01,532
不是被我的朋友殺死的
Not by my friends.

740
01:05:01,606 --> 01:05:03,267
是被我
By me.

741
01:05:12,116 --> 01:05:13,640
啊!
Aaah!

742
01:05:47,852 --> 01:05:49,319
你們曾是戀人
You were lovers.

743
01:06:03,233 --> 01:06:04,723
[Door closes]

744
01:06:07,472 --> 01:06:10,032
地下組織是我們的反對者
The Underground is our foe,

745
01:06:10,108 --> 01:06:12,668
比那些拒用情感控制劑的人
and greater than even the threat

746
01:06:12,744 --> 01:06:16,612
對我們的威脅大得多的是
of those who have forsaken their Prozium for emotion

747
01:06:16,681 --> 01:06:21,778
一群聯合在一起的情感犯
is the threat of those selfsame individuals united.

748
01:06:21,853 --> 01:06:24,617
他們是個秘密組織...
They are the secret organization...

749
01:06:30,161 --> 01:06:33,096
所以,神父下了手諭
And thus, it is in the writing of the Father

750
01:06:33,164 --> 01:06:34,927
要我們找出我們最大的...
that we find our greatest...

751
01:06:36,801 --> 01:06:38,666
下午好,長官
Good afternoon, sir.

752
01:06:38,736 --> 01:06:41,637
您來是想要什麼?
What will it be for you?

753
01:06:41,706 --> 01:06:43,435
最新的控制劑?
The latest copy of the inserts?

754
01:06:43,507 --> 01:06:45,668
更新的宣言?
Revised edition of the manifesto?

755
01:06:45,743 --> 01:06:46,767
艾洛·帕崔吉
Errol Partridge.

756
01:06:46,844 --> 01:06:49,404
你知道些他的什麼情況?
What do you know about him?

757
01:06:49,480 --> 01:06:50,811
您說什麼?
I beg your pardon?

758
01:06:50,881 --> 01:06:52,746
都出去,快點
Everyone out. Now.

759
01:07:06,597 --> 01:07:08,531
我再問你一次
I'm gonna ask you one more time.

760
01:07:08,599 --> 01:07:11,227
艾洛·帕崔吉... 你知道他些什麼情況?
Errol Partridge... what do you know about him?

761
01:07:11,302 --> 01:07:14,169
您肯定是弄錯了...
I'm sure this must be some mis...

762
01:07:14,238 --> 01:07:16,502
- 你是個情感犯 - 我不是
- You're an offender. - I'm not.

763
01:07:16,574 --> 01:07:19,441
不是? 那你為什麼這麼怕我?
No? Then why are you so scared of me?

764
01:07:19,510 --> 01:07:22,570
現在,你得告訴我你所知道的 艾洛·帕崔吉的所有情況
Now, you will tell me everything you know about Errol Partridge,

765
01:07:22,646 --> 01:07:24,580
不然我就把你抓起來
or I will have a wagon come to take you

766
01:07:24,648 --> 01:07:27,481
送去毀滅堂燒掉
to the Hall of Destruction for summary combustion.

767
01:07:27,551 --> 01:07:29,678
我...真的不知道...
[Breathing heavily] L-I really don't know...

768
01:07:29,754 --> 01:07:30,846
說!
Speak!

769
01:07:30,955 --> 01:07:34,516
他...他曾經跟一個叫吉根的人一起來過
He... he'd come in here with a fellow named Jurgen.

770
01:07:34,592 --> 01:07:35,854
為什麼來?
Why?

771
01:07:35,926 --> 01:07:39,020
我...我就知道這麼多,我發誓
That's... that's all I know. I swear.

772
01:07:39,096 --> 01:07:40,085
吉根!
Jurgen!

773
01:08:00,818 --> 01:08:02,615
有意思
Interesting.

774
01:08:04,455 --> 01:08:05,820
- 呃-哦! - 呃!
- Ugh-ow! - Ugh!

775
01:08:07,123 --> 01:08:09,489
[Groans]

776
01:08:11,594 --> 01:08:14,085
[Gun cocks]

777
01:08:40,658 --> 01:08:43,718
我們監視你很久了, 培斯頓
We've been watching you, Preston.

778
01:08:49,934 --> 01:08:51,231
你是吉根
You're Jurgen.

779
01:08:52,837 --> 01:08:55,567
你有情感
You're feeling.

780
01:09:09,954 --> 01:09:12,047
知道你為什麼要來嗎?
Do you know why you came?

781
01:09:17,727 --> 01:09:20,218
[Buzzes]

782
01:09:34,745 --> 01:09:37,339
歡迎來到地下
Welcome to the Underground.

783
01:09:47,825 --> 01:09:49,349
波動器
Polygraph.

784
01:09:49,426 --> 01:09:53,362
它能探測人情感的波動
It detects fluctuations of human emotion.

785
01:09:53,430 --> 01:09:55,591
我們必須要肯定
We have to be sure.

786
01:10:00,738 --> 01:10:02,228
瑪麗
Mary.

787
01:10:08,746 --> 01:10:10,907
你左口袋裡有
You're carrying in your left pocket

788
01:10:10,981 --> 01:10:13,916
帶著她的體香的紅絲帶
a red ribbon sprayed with her scent.

789
01:10:16,186 --> 01:10:18,051
在你覺得沒有人會看到的地方
You breathe it in sometimes

790
01:10:18,122 --> 01:10:21,023
你會時不時的聞聞它
when you think there's no one to see.

791
01:10:21,091 --> 01:10:25,027
但是你的情感...
But what you feel...

792
01:10:25,095 --> 01:10:27,620
你的情感只有
what you feel could only be satisfied

793
01:10:27,698 --> 01:10:30,326
在你全心愛上她的時候 才能得到滿足
by falling yourself into her.

794
01:10:35,973 --> 01:10:39,238
她已經被安排焚化了...
She's scheduled for combustion...

795
01:10:39,310 --> 01:10:41,471
明天
tomorrow.

796
01:10:47,351 --> 01:10:49,478
我知道
I know.

797
01:10:50,854 --> 01:10:53,186
你知道,我很像你
You know, I was like you.

798
01:10:53,257 --> 01:10:57,216
但是你需要瞭解的關於 情感的第一件事
But the first thing you learn about emotion

799
01:10:57,294 --> 01:10:59,660
就是它有它的代價...
is that it has its price...

800
01:10:59,730 --> 01:11:02,631
就像個潘多拉魔盒
a complete paradox.

801
01:11:02,700 --> 01:11:05,567
但是沒有壓抑...
But without restraint...

802
01:11:05,636 --> 01:11:07,866
沒有控制...
without control...

803
01:11:07,938 --> 01:11:09,872
情感就是混亂
