Take him to the Hall of Destruction

1002
01:26:03,801 --> 01:26:06,065
進行審判和焚化
for summary judgment and combustion.

1003
01:26:06,136 --> 01:26:08,570
等一下,等一下,聽我解釋啊
Wait, wait, wait. Wait! I can explain this.

1004
01:26:08,639 --> 01:26:11,767
呃,長官,我沒有情感!
Uh, sir, I'm not feeling!

1005
01:26:11,842 --> 01:26:14,242
他才是有情感的!
He is the one who's feeling!

1006
01:26:14,311 --> 01:26:15,869
你們搞錯了!
This is a mistake!

1007
01:26:17,981 --> 01:26:19,778
當然...
Of course...

1008
01:26:19,850 --> 01:26:22,751
既然有人提出申訴
since a complaint has been lodged,

1009
01:26:22,820 --> 01:26:25,721
根據法典我會派一組人
law and the letter is that I allow a team

1010
01:26:25,789 --> 01:26:28,223
去搜查你們的住處
to carry out the search of your premises.

1011
01:26:28,292 --> 01:26:30,419
你覺得那有必要嗎, 教士?
Do you think that's entirely necessary, Cleric,

1012
01:26:30,494 --> 01:26:34,487
或者是我太...謹慎了?
or am I being too... exacting?

1013
01:26:34,565 --> 01:26:36,931
我聽您的,長官
As you say, sir,

1014
01:26:37,000 --> 01:26:38,934
根據法典來吧
it's the law and the letter.

1015
01:26:39,002 --> 01:26:41,994
你的一個同事走到了盡頭
And it doesn't disturb you in the least

1016
01:26:42,072 --> 01:26:44,438
你一點都不覺得不安嗎?
that your colleague is going to his end?

1017
01:26:44,508 --> 01:26:46,942
我唯一覺得不安的事是,長官
The only thing that disturbs me, sir,

1018
01:26:47,010 --> 01:26:49,706
我雖然身為神父對付地下組織的一個工具
is that I am Father's instrument against the Underground,

1019
01:26:49,780 --> 01:26:54,945
但是...我至今未有機會面見他老人家
and yet... I've never had the honor of meeting him.

1020
01:26:55,018 --> 01:26:56,918
呣...
Hmm.

1021
01:26:57,020 --> 01:26:58,681
是的.但是,教士,你知道
Yes, but, Cleric, you know

1022
01:26:58,756 --> 01:27:01,850
神父從來不接見任何人
that Father never grants an audience to anyone.

1023
01:27:01,925 --> 01:27:04,257
即使是給他查出叛軍的人?
Even to the man who brings him the Resistance?

1024
01:27:15,070 --> 01:27:16,662
[Tires screech]

1025
01:27:16,740 --> 01:27:18,401
對不起,長官,例行檢查
Sorry, sir. Just a formality.

1026
01:27:18,475 --> 01:27:20,602
搜索隊馬上就到
The search team will be up momentarily.

1027
01:27:20,677 --> 01:27:23,271
很好,我沒什麼好隱藏的
Excellent. I have nothing to hide.

1028
01:27:43,367 --> 01:27:45,562
搜索隊已經在裡面了,長官
The search teams are already inside, sir.

1029
01:27:45,636 --> 01:27:46,933
很好
- [Beeps] - Excellent.

1030
01:27:47,002 --> 01:27:49,266
[Men speaking indistinctly in distance]

1031
01:28:07,791 --> 01:28:10,089
在找東西嗎?
ROBBIE: Looking for something?

1032
01:28:14,865 --> 01:28:16,628
如果我是你...
If I were you...

1033
01:28:16,700 --> 01:28:21,763
我以後會更小心一點
I'd be more careful in the future.

1034
01:28:26,877 --> 01:28:28,242
多長時間了?
How long?

1035
01:28:28,312 --> 01:28:30,576
從媽媽死後就開始了
Since Mom.

1036
01:28:33,550 --> 01:28:34,642
麗莎呢?
And Lisa?

1037
01:28:34,718 --> 01:28:35,980
當然了
Of course.

1038
01:28:40,757 --> 01:28:42,418
你怎麼知道的?
How did you know?

1039
01:28:42,492 --> 01:28:45,017
你忘記了...
You forget...

1040
01:28:45,095 --> 01:28:47,495
我的工作就是知道你的思想
it's my job to know what you're thinking.

1041
01:28:50,734 --> 01:28:53,168
那你知道我現在要做什麼了
Then you know what I'm gonna do now.

1042
01:28:55,370 --> 01:28:55,372


1043
01:28:55,373 --> 01:28:58,740
你有話要跟副主席說嗎?
You have a message for the Vice-Council?

1044
01:28:58,809 --> 01:29:00,674
任務完成了
It's done.

1045
01:29:00,745 --> 01:29:04,146
我找到叛軍基地
I've located the Resistance.

1046
01:29:04,215 --> 01:29:06,547
馬上過來
Come now.

1047
01:29:06,617 --> 01:29:08,608
就能全殲他們
You'll have them all.

1048
01:29:30,541 --> 01:29:34,068
在神父跟你說話之前不要先跟他說話
Do not address Father unless first addressed by him.

1049
01:29:34,145 --> 01:29:35,407
不要直視他
Avoid eye contact.

1050
01:29:35,479 --> 01:29:38,710
如果你闖進了他的個人安全區
If you should break his personal security zone,

1051
01:29:38,783 --> 01:29:41,308
你將馬上被狙擊手槍殺
you will be immediately put down by snipers.

1052
01:29:41,385 --> 01:29:43,046
明白了嗎?
Is that understood?

1053
01:29:43,120 --> 01:29:46,248
當然,你要交出你的武器
You'll be required to surrender your firearm, of course,

1054
01:29:46,323 --> 01:29:48,257
然後還要進行一次測試
and then there's the test.

1055
01:29:48,325 --> 01:29:49,690
測試?
Test?

1056
01:29:50,694 --> 01:29:53,128
是的
Yes.

1057
01:29:53,197 --> 01:29:56,223
不能想像我們能讓神父
You didn't imagine we would risk exposing Father

1058
01:29:56,300 --> 01:29:58,734
與一個即使像你這樣忠實的下屬接觸
to even such a dedicated servant as yourself

1059
01:29:58,803 --> 01:30:02,102
而不對你進行測試, 對不對?
without first having tested you, did you?

1060
01:30:05,943 --> 01:30:07,672
請
Please.

1061
01:30:07,742 --> 01:30:09,437
[Mechanical whirring]

1062
01:30:17,919 --> 01:30:21,480
[Man speaking indistinctly]

1063
01:30:21,559 --> 01:30:23,049
教士...
Cleric...

1064
01:30:23,127 --> 01:30:25,095
請交出你的武器
your weapon, please.

1065
01:30:29,633 --> 01:30:31,658
這邊
Here.

1066
01:30:36,607 --> 01:30:37,733
請坐
Sit.

1067
01:30:41,078 --> 01:30:43,342
我們先從一個測試問題開始
We'll start with a test question first.

1068
01:30:43,414 --> 01:30:46,747
事實上更像是個謎語
[Snaps fingers] More of a riddle, actually.

1069
01:30:48,118 --> 01:30:50,245
你要說的是用什麼方法最簡單
What would you say is the easiest way

1070
01:30:50,321 --> 01:30:52,551
能從一個耶和華教士手裡取到武器?
to get a weapon away from a Grammaton Cleric?

1071
01:30:52,621 --> 01:30:55,556
[Guns cocking]

1072
01:30:58,062 --> 01:31:00,656
你找他要
You ask him for it.

1073
01:31:07,905 --> 01:31:10,840
我告訴我你我會靠你成就我的事業的,教士
I told you I'd make my career with you, Cleric.

1074
01:31:14,311 --> 01:31:15,608
...去組織力量...
...to combine the capacity...

1075
01:31:17,481 --> 01:31:18,470
培斯頓...
Preston...

1076
01:31:18,549 --> 01:31:21,017
勃蘭特的任務很簡單...
Brandt's job was simple...

1077
01:31:21,085 --> 01:31:23,576
讓你覺得自己贏了
to make you feel like you'd won,

1078
01:31:23,654 --> 01:31:26,817
讓你覺得安全
to make you feel safe.

1079
01:31:30,027 --> 01:31:33,554
許多年來,我試圖安插一個內線
For years, I tried to infiltrate an agent

1080
01:31:33,631 --> 01:31:35,155
到地下組織裡...
into the Underground...

1081
01:31:36,567 --> 01:31:38,626
...直到我發現了你...
...until it hit me...

1082
01:31:38,702 --> 01:31:42,433
為了進入他們中間而不被發現
in order to pass undetected into their midst,

1083
01:31:42,506 --> 01:31:45,236
為了取得他們的信任
in order to be trusted by them,

1084
01:31:45,309 --> 01:31:50,679
我的內線必須要想他們所想
my provocateur would have to think like them

1085
01:31:50,748 --> 01:31:53,649
並且必須要感受他們所感
and would have to feel like them.

1086
01:31:53,717 --> 01:31:56,652
但是到哪兒去找這樣一個人...
But where to find such a man...

1087
01:31:56,720 --> 01:32:02,022
一個有能力感覺他從未感覺到的情感?
a man with the capacity to feel who didn't yet know it?

1088
01:32:04,962 --> 01:32:07,658
但是...
But...

1089
01:32:07,731 --> 01:32:08,993
我們從來沒見過面
we've never met.

1090
01:32:09,066 --> 01:32:10,897
沒有?
No?

1091
01:32:15,940 --> 01:32:18,465
別這麼驚訝, 培斯頓
Don't look so surprised, Preston.

1092
01:32:18,542 --> 01:32:20,407
為什麼神父要比
Why should Father be more real

1093
01:32:20,477 --> 01:32:22,945
其他的政治木偶更真實?
than any other political puppet?

1094
01:32:23,013 --> 01:32:25,948
真正的神父幾年前就死了
The real Father died years ago.

1095
01:32:26,016 --> 01:32:27,950
教會只是選舉我
The Council simply elected me

1096
01:32:28,018 --> 01:32:30,919
來繼承他的事業
to pursue his paternal tradition.

1097
01:32:31,021 --> 01:32:33,114
還有你, 培斯頓
And you, Preston,

1098
01:32:33,190 --> 01:32:36,057
叛軍想像中的救世主
the supposed savior of the Resistance,

1099
01:32:36,126 --> 01:32:37,991
現在成了他們的毀滅者
are now its destroyer,

1100
01:32:38,062 --> 01:32:42,829
還有,跟他們一起,你自己也露出了原形...
and, along with them, you've given me yourself...

1101
01:32:42,900 --> 01:32:44,561
冷靜的...
calmly...

1102
01:32:44,635 --> 01:32:46,500
沉著的...
cooly...

1103
01:32:46,570 --> 01:32:51,303
完全不出意外的
entirely without incident.

1104
01:32:51,373 --> 01:32:54,274
[Polygraph machine scribbling rapidly]

1105
01:32:55,412 --> 01:32:57,039
不
No.

1106
01:32:57,112 --> 01:32:58,545
[Beeping]

1107
01:32:58,616 --> 01:32:59,583
哦...
Oh...

1108
01:33:00,384 --> 01:33:01,544
媽的
Shit.

1109
01:33:03,520 --> 01:33:05,215
不是不出意外
Not without incident.

1110
01:33:12,229 --> 01:33:13,719
我來了
I'm coming.

1111
01:34:42,687 --> 01:34:44,552
你真該學會敲門的
You really should learn to knock.

1112
01:35:11,115 --> 01:35:14,482
感覺怎麼樣, 培斯頓?
How did it feel, Preston?

1113
01:35:22,190 --> 01:35:24,852
[Growls softly]

1114
01:35:28,099 --> 01:35:30,329
- 啊! - 呃! 呃! 呃-啊!
- Agh! - Ugh! Ugh! Uhh-ah!

1115
01:35:32,236 --> 01:35:33,635
哇!
Wah!

1116
01:35:33,704 --> 01:35:35,365
呃! 啊! 呃!
Ugh! Agh! Uhh!

1117
01:35:35,439 --> 01:35:36,997
呃!
Ugh!

1118
01:35:38,209 --> 01:35:39,335
呃!
Ugh!

1119
01:35:39,410 --> 01:35:41,435
- 啊! - 啊!
- Aggh! - Aggh!

1120
01:35:55,259 --> 01:35:58,092
注意我的制服, 教士
Mind the uniform, Cleric.

1121
01:36:00,094 --> 01:36:02,062
[Whooshing]

1122
01:36:03,701 --> 01:36:06,864
我準備穿很長時間的
I plan to be wearing it for a long time.

1123
01:36:29,757 --> 01:36:31,622
[Thud]

1124
01:36:42,673 --> 01:36:45,369
小心點, 培斯頓
Be careful, Preston.

1125
01:36:45,443 --> 01:36:47,809
"你踩在我的夢想之翼上"
You're treading on my dreams.

1126
01:37:22,880 --> 01:37:24,177
哦!
Ohh!

1127
01:37:24,248 --> 01:37:26,011
等一下!
Wait!

1128
01:37:26,083 --> 01:37:27,107
等一下!
Wait.

1129
01:37:27,184 --> 01:37:28,617
看著我
Look at me.

1130
01:37:28,686 --> 01:37:29,778
看著我
Look at me.

1131
01:37:29,817 --> 01:37:31,808
[Breathing heavily]

1132
01:37:31,922 --> 01:37:33,583
我是活生生的
I'm life.

1133
01:37:33,657 --> 01:37:37,149
我活著,我呼吸...
I live, l-I breathe...

1134
01:37:37,191 --> 01:37:39,125
[Breathes deeply]

1135
01:37:39,230 --> 01:37:40,697
我有感覺
I feel.

1136
01:37:42,733 --> 01:37:45,531
現在你知道了...
Now that you know it...

1137
01:37:45,603 --> 01:37:48,401
你真的能下得了手嗎?
can you really take it?

1138
01:37:48,472 --> 01:37:50,497
這真的值得嗎?
Is it really worth the price?

1139
01:37:56,614 --> 01:37:58,343
我很樂意承受
I pay it gladly.

1140
01:38:00,415 --> 01:38:02,781
[Thud]

1141
01:38:17,067 --> 01:38:20,503
以下內容被定級為EC-10 ...
The following items have been rated EC-10...

1142
01:38:20,571 --> 01:38:21,902
有罪的
condemned.

1143
01:38:21,936 --> 01:38:24,234
[Speaking indistinctly]

1144
01:38:27,108 --> 01:38:28,769
[Thud]

1145
01:38:28,879 --> 01:38:30,039
在19世紀...
In the 19th century...

1146
01:38:33,414 --> 01:38:36,508
[All shouting indistinctly]

1147
01:38:36,620 --> 01:38:39,350
...世界臣服在它的腳下
...world to its knees.

1148
01:38:39,423 --> 01:38:43,223
二千年以前...
Two millennia ago...

1149
01:38:43,294 --> 01:38:44,955
在征服已知世界的過程中
in his conquest of the known world,

1150
01:38:45,029 --> 01:38:46,553
亞歷山大大帝屠殺了
Alexander the Great slaughtered

1151
01:38:46,630 --> 01:38:49,258
超過100萬人
more than one million human beings.

1152
01:38:50,901 --> 01:38:54,337
3個世紀後,只是出於嫉妒
Three centuries later, purely out of jealousy,

1153
01:38:54,405 --> 01:38:57,670
蓋斯·凱撒, "卡利古拉" 謀殺了他的親妹妹
Gaius Germanicus, "Caligula," murdered his own sister,

1154
01:38:57,741 --> 01:39:00,437
懷著他的親生骨肉
impregnated with his own child.

1155
01:39:00,511 --> 01:39:01,637
在...
In the...

1156
01:39:02,110 --> 01:39:04,203
[Electricity crackles]

1157
01:39:09,450 --> 01:39:11,714
[Speaking indistinctly, echoing]

1158
01:39:12,823 --> 01:39:15,758
以下內容被定級為EC-10 ...
...items have been rated EC-10...

1159
01:39:17,661 --> 01:39:19,891
...定級為有罪的,毀滅的
...rated condemned, destroyed.

1160
01:39:19,927 --> 01:39:21,792
[Sputtering]

1161
01:39:22,666 --> 01:39:24,896
...內容被定級為...
...items have been rated...

1162
01:39:24,932 --> 01:39:27,127
[Silence]

1163
01:39:32,940 --> 01:39:35,374
[Rumbling]

1164
01:39:39,947 --> 01:39:42,074
[Rumbling continues]

1165
01:39:54,829 --> 01:39:57,696
[Indistinct shouting, gunfire]

1166
01:40:00,334 --> 01:40:02,131
[Shouting continues]

1167
01:40:10,111 --> 01:40:13,137
[Men cheering]

1168
01:40:35,770 --> 01:40:39,638
[Slow instrumental music plays]

1169
01:40:44,679 --> 01:40:47,705
[Indistinct singing]

1170
01:42:26,147 --> 01:42:29,173
[Tempo quickens]

1171
01:43:35,783 --> 01:43:38,809
[Tempo slows]

1172
01:45:31,565 --> 01:45:34,762
[Mid-tempo music plays]

1173
01:46:19,113 --> 01:46:22,139
[Techno music plays]

1174
01:46:45,239 --> 01:46:47,605
[Tempo slows]

1175
01:46:58,219 --> 01:47:00,710
[Music ends]
